      "content": "I see. So you're saying the \"vibrant\" or \"communal\" aspects of B and C make them less suitable for a luxury brand? Could you expand on why someone looking for \"refinement\" would specifically avoid a neighborhood like Heritage Square with its high-end cultural architecture and deep history?",
